      "text": "![](https://eecsis.mit.edu/images/fall.gif): only offered fall term ![](https://eecsis.mit.edu/images/spring.gif): only offered spring term grey: not offered this academic year."
    },
    {
      "id": "5",
      "text": "If your primary major is 6-14, at most three of your economics subjects may count toward the eight-subject HASS requirement."
    },
    {
      "id": "6",
      "text": "16.0002/18.0002/CSE.01 are acceptable alternatives to 6.0002"
    }
